        {
            "title": "午後再上 滬指收升50點 深指漲1.95% 寧德時代回穩",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後大玩過山車，未礙內地股市持續向好，滬深兩市股指齊升逾1%收市；之前連跌兩日的寧德時代(03750)A股(300750.SZ)亦回穩。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早高開10點後便展現升軌，開市不足半小時升幅已擴大至超過30點，其後一直在3910點之上徘徊，午後升越早市高位，尾市最高曾見3933點，升51點或1.33%；滬指最後收報3931點，升50點或1.3%，成交9678.54億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全程跑贏，早市出現的全日低位13666點時仍漲130點或0.96%，早市中段一度衝上13835點，將升幅擴大至298點或2.2%，其後便進入在13700點至13835點之間橫行的格局；深指收報13801點，升264點或1.95%，成交1.21萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也升62點或1.4%，以4537點收市；創業板指數漲65點或2.01%，報3316點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股升多跌少，寧德時代A股連跌兩日後於今早仍幾乎全程「潛水」，午後回穩呈好淡爭持，一度倒升0.88%；收報397.81元，微升0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">昨天結束七連跌並重返千元關口的寒武紀(688256.SH)，今日再升1.02%，收報1039元。藍思科技(06613)A股(300433.SZ)也升5%，報29.4元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">復星醫藥(02196)績後A、H齊升，H股在下午約3時升3.84%，復星醫藥A股(600196.SH)漲4.32%，報25.36元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15789873-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e4%b8%8a-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%8750%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b21-95-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e5%9b%9e%e7%a9%a9",
